tor-typed_2.13:1.1.5\",\n      \"scope\": \"testImplementation\",\n      \"reason\": \"Official Pekko HTTP examples create a typed ActorSystem and recommend adding pekko-actor-typed with pekko-stream and pekko-http.\"\n    }\n  ],\n  \"agent_guidance\": \"No Docker image or environment/system property appears necessary. Tests should create a local ActorSystem, bind only to localhost using an ephemeral port when starting a server, avoid stdin/fixed-port examples, and always unbind and terminate the ActorSystem in cleanup/finally code.\",\n  \"risks\": [\n    \"If tests leave the ActorSystem running, Gradle/native test execution can hang due to Pekko threads.\",\n    \"Scala/Pekko native-image behavior may still require metadata adjustments; local Gradle and Native Image verification remain authoritative.\"\n  ]\n}", "textSignature": "{\"v\":1,\"id\":\"msg_0eb4d07ac354c790016a2b5c2bb42c8194a3967e9218e783b3\",\"phase\":\"final_answer\"}"}], "api": "openai-responses", "provider": "OCA", "model": "oca/gpt-5.5", "usage": {"input": 1316, "output": 847, "cacheRead": 26112, "cacheWrite": 0, "totalTokens": 28275, "cost": {"input": 0, "output": 0, "cacheRead": 0, "cacheWrite": 0, "total": 0}}, "stopReason": "stop", "timestamp": 1781226525193, "responseId": "resp_0eb4d07ac354c790016a2b5c1df1988194b497f4b6f0e6cee8"}}
